title: Welcome to Jeff Bakalar's Brain
itunes:title: Welcome to Jeff Bakalar's Brain
description:
This week: Alex regales us with stories of the greatest little shop in upstate New York, we played the Cuphead DLC, The Quarry, and Last Call BBS, God of War Ragnarok gets a release date, Destiny gets a mobile game (maybe), and we answer some of your emails (?!?). Plus, you won't believe which famous country singer got her own pinball machine!

Advertise on The Nextlander Podcast at Gumball.fm, or support us on Patreon!

CHAPTERS

(00:00:46) Alex making the most of his vacation-ish
(00:03:38) What is your Rock Fantasy?

(00:35:56) First Break
(00:36:00) Last Call BBS [PC (Microsoft Windows)] on Jul 05, 2022
(00:52:10) The Quarry [PC (Microsoft Windows), PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One] on Jun 10, 2022
(01:07:31) Neon White [PC (Microsoft Windows), Nintendo Switch] on Jun 16, 2022
(01:13:25) Second Break
(01:13:29) News
(01:13:30) God of War Ragnarok gets a date
(01:18:27) Forspoken gets a new date
(01:26:48) No Red Dead or GTA IV remasters in the near future
(01:29:46) Destiny is getting a mobile game?

(01:40:28) It's time for emails!
(02:13:56) Wrapping up and new Nextlander content
(02:15:25) Mysterious Benefactor Tier Shoutouts
